org.dexpi.pid.xml

Class Association

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dexpi.pid.xml.Association

  • public class Association
extends java.lang.Object
    An Association references other objects either by ID, Name or Tag attribute. If ID elements are persistent (see PlantModel element) then ID references may be to items not in this file.
